title: Sugar Shack Diner
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. American-style burger place with limited seating. Has one vegetarian/vegan menu page with burgers, fries, vegan cheese, and gluten free options; vegan desserts like a brownie with ice cream and whipped cream or the orea freak shake with chocolate sauce, ice cream, and brownie pieces. Changing menu with special vegan burgers and desserts.
